                                            </li>
                                            <li style="margin-bottom:5px;">
                                                <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height:35px; text-align:justify">To engage in activity in relation to our member services. This may include sending you newsletters, updates, event invitations and other information that may be of interest to you.</p>
                                            </li>
                                            <li style="margin-bottom:5px;">
                                                <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height:35px; text-align:justify">Where you have applied for a position with us, to review and process your job application.</p>
