                                                <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height:35px; text-align:justify">To collate, process and share any statistics based on an aggregation of information held by us, provided that any individual is not identified from the resulting analysis and the collation, processing and dissemination of such information is permitted by law.</p>
