                                    <div class="title-box text-left">
                                        <h3 style="line-height: 1.2; font-size:1.5rem">How we share information with third parties</h3>
                                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height:35px; text-align:justify">We share personal information with our offices around the world and the various companies and entities that make up our global network. As a result, your personal information may be transferred to locations outside Nigeria as well as within it for the purposes described above.</p>
                                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height:35px; text-align:justify">We may also share your personal information outside TMC. This may include:</p>

                                        <ul class="iq-lister column-1">
                                            <li style="margin-bottom:5px;">
                                                <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height:35px; text-align:justify">Third party agents/suppliers or contractors, bound by obligations of confidentiality, in connection with the processing of your personal information for the purposes described in this Policy. This may include, but is not limited to, IT and communications service providers.</p>
                                            </li>
                                            <li style="margin-bottom:5px;">
                                                <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height:35px; text-align:justify">Third parties relevant to the services that we provide. This may include, but is not limited to, counterparties to litigation, professional service providers, sponsors of our events, regulators, authorities and governmental institutions.</p>
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="title-box text-left">
                                        <h3 style="line-height: 1.2; font-size:1.5rem">Keeping your information and information security</h3>
                                        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height:35px; text-align:justify">How long we hold your personal information for will vary and will depend principally on:</p>
                                        
                                        <ul class="iq-lister column-1">
